reviewText: Not bad. I just felt like there was a certain something missing. I've watched it only once- very unusual for me with train videos. Now if you didn't make it to Spencer, like I did not, then this does show you what went on. And that's what I'm judging it on.
Can't wait to see my husbands face when he opens this. He was there 3 days in a row and even though he took thousands of pictures, this will be special.
